---
// ContactInvitation.astro
---
<section class="py-32 lg:py-48 bg-[#f9f8f6] text-[#1a1a1a] relative rounded-none">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
      
      <!-- Left Column: The Invitation -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-serif font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 leading-[1.1]">
          Let's Build Something <span class="italic font-light">Extraordinary.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#1a1a1a]/80 font-sans tracking-wide max-w-lg">
          At TORVIX, we bring visionary architectural concepts to life. Our execution is defined by uncompromising precision, transforming raw blueprints into breathtaking realities of quiet luxury.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: The Details -->
      <div class="reveal delay-200">
        <div class="flex flex-col border-t border-slate-200 font-sans tracking-wide">
          
          <div class="py-8 border-b border-slate-200 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between group">
            <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2 sm:mb-0 w-32">Call Us</span>
            <a href="tel:+18001234567" class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl hover:text-slate-600 transition-colors duration-300">
              +1 (800) 123-4567
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="py-8 border-b border-slate-200 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between group">
            <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2 sm:mb-0 w-32">Email</span>
            <a href="mailto:studio@torvix.com" class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl hover:text-slate-600 transition-colors duration-300">
              studio@torvix.com
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="py-8 border-b border-slate-200 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between group">
            <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2 sm:mb-0 w-32">Instagram</span>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/torvix.design" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl hover:text-slate-600 transition-colors duration-300">
              @torvix.design
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="py-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start justify-between group">
            <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2 sm:mb-0 w-32 mt-1">Office</span>
            <span class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl sm:text-right max-w-[280px]">
              123 Architecture Blvd,<br/> Design District
            </span>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
